      "strengths_deep_dive": [
        "Support Life Foundation demonstrates a commitment to transparency and accountability, earning a <cite id=\"13\">Platinum Seal of Transparency from Candid</cite>. This level of disclosure is paired with a <cite id=\"14\">perfect score of 100 in Culture & Community</cite> from Charity Navigator. Their operational model is highly direct, focusing on capacity building and direct aid such as <cite id=\"15\">Hot Meals and Project Educate</cite>. By maintaining a small <cite id=\"16\">board of 3 members</cite> and a lean staff, they ensure that the vast majority of their <cite id=\"3\">$1.2 million in revenue</cite> is deployed directly to their humanitarian missions in the US and West Africa."
      ],
      "summary": "Support Life Foundation is a community-based organization founded in <cite id=\"1\">2017</cite> that focuses on social and economic justice. The charity operates with a lean model designed to <cite id=\"2\">minimize costs while providing essential services</cite> to underserved populations. In the 2023 fiscal year, the organization reported <cite id=\"3\">total revenue of $1,228,678</cite>, which was primarily driven by public contributions. Their work spans both domestic and international humanitarian efforts, including programs in <cite id=\"4\">California, Sierra Leone, and Cameroon</cite>. Domestically, they serve multiple counties in Northern and Central California, including <cite id=\"5\">Oakland, Sacramento, and Fresno</cite>. Their international initiatives are diverse, ranging from the <cite id=\"6\">Health Center Yaound\u00e9</cite> to the <cite id=\"7\">Teacher For Every Village</cite> program. Financially, the charity maintains a high level of efficiency, directing <cite id=\"8\">95.1% of its expenses toward programs</cite>. This efficiency is further highlighted by their fundraising strategy, which reports <cite id=\"9\">$0.00 spent to raise every $1</cite> in donations. While the organization has seen significant revenue fluctuations, including a <cite id=\"10\">3-year revenue CAGR of -22.8%</cite>, it maintains <cite id=\"11\">7.1 months of working capital</cite>, providing a solid buffer for its ongoing operations.",
